426
00:22:22,010 --> 00:22:23,020
Cheers!

427
00:22:23,610 --> 00:22:24,670
That's all?

428
00:22:25,490 --> 00:22:26,510
Don't you have anything else to say?

429
00:22:27,490 --> 00:22:28,910
