432
00:22:34,890 --> 00:22:36,230
Well,

433
00:22:36,650 --> 00:22:38,760
I was being nosy.

434
00:22:38,850 --> 00:22:41,150
However, I still don't get it.

435
00:22:41,250 --> 00:22:43,070
Why did you get so angry?

436
00:22:43,250 --> 00:22:45,550
Just because Xiao Jun's mum
doesn't like flowers?

437
00:22:46,090 --> 00:22:47,120
She likes flowers.

438
00:22:47,210 --> 00:22:48,510
However, it has nothing to do with me.

439
00:22:49,730 --> 00:22:51,350
Both of you...

440
00:22:52,250 --> 00:22:53,710
It's been so many years.

441
00:22:54,730 --> 00:22:56,110
You've been taking care of them.

442
00:22:56,650 --> 00:22:57,870
So what?

443
00:22:57,970 --> 00:23:00,150
Does it have to involve a love affair?

444
00:23:02,050 --> 00:23:03,520
Do I have to date her

445
00:23:03,610 --> 00:23:04,620
and marry her?

446
00:23:05,010 --> 00:23:06,470
What if I'm taking care of them

447
00:23:06,600 --> 00:23:07,910
as Luo Liang's comrade?

448
00:23:08,930 --> 00:23:11,430
I'm just pretending to be Xiao Jun's dad.

449
00:23:11,970 --> 00:23:13,910
I'll take care of them and protect them

450
00:23:14,250 --> 00:23:15,530
until Xiao Jun grows up,

451
00:23:15,610 --> 00:23:17,030
until he's grown into
an independent adult,

452
00:23:17,160 --> 00:23:19,190
until they don't need
my protection anymore,

453
00:23:19,330 --> 00:23:20,710
until he can protect his own mum.

454
00:23:20,890 --> 00:23:21,780
Is that not allowed?

455
00:23:24,890 --> 00:23:26,550
I'm not avoiding it.

456
00:23:26,930 --> 00:23:28,000
It's to the contrary.

457
00:23:28,090 --> 00:23:29,380
I'm facing it.

458
00:23:35,610 --> 00:23:36,630
I got it now.

459
00:23:38,090 --> 00:23:39,060
Liang Mu Ze.

460
00:23:39,690 --> 00:23:41,670
I didn't mean to

461
00:23:41,850 --> 00:23:43,670
embarrass you on purpose.

462
00:23:44,050 --> 00:23:44,950
Firstly,

463
00:23:45,090 --> 00:23:47,070
as Xiao Jun's doctor in charge,

464
00:23:47,330 --> 00:23:49,320
