emotionally agitated.

465
00:23:49,400 --> 00:23:50,990
It will affect his recovery.

466
00:23:51,930 --> 00:23:53,140
More importantly,

467
00:23:53,570 --> 00:23:55,510
I don't want you two to let
each other slip by.

468
00:23:57,170 --> 00:23:58,540
I know the feeling.

469
00:24:04,010 --> 00:24:04,730
I mean,

470
00:24:04,810 --> 00:24:06,670
letting each other slip by
when the feeling is mutual.

471
00:24:07,370 --> 00:24:07,960
It's

472
00:24:08,050 --> 00:24:09,100
quite disheartening.

473
00:24:12,930 --> 00:24:14,440
Therefore, I promised Xiao Jun

474
00:24:14,530 --> 00:24:15,990
to buy a bouquet in your name.

475
00:24:16,410 --> 00:24:17,440
However, I didn't expect

476
00:24:17,530 --> 00:24:19,310
it would bother you that much.

477
00:24:21,890 --> 00:24:22,990
I'm sorry.

478
00:24:23,520 --> 00:24:25,270
I was full of myself.

479
00:24:25,530 --> 00:24:27,230
That's why I misunderstood you two.

480
00:24:34,410 --> 00:24:35,510
