508
00:25:55,970 --> 00:25:57,290
If there is nothing between them,

509
00:25:57,370 --> 00:25:58,240
why did Captain Liang

510
00:25:58,330 --> 00:25:59,610
bring her back to camp?

511
00:25:59,690 --> 00:26:01,070
She stayed here for so many days.

512
00:26:02,810 --> 00:26:03,690
Xiang Yang.

513
00:26:04,450 --> 00:26:07,150
"The west is veiled in rain
while the east enjoys sunshine."

514
00:26:07,850 --> 00:26:12,710
"My gallant is as deep in love
as the day is fine."

515
00:26:32,130 --> 00:26:33,560
Xia Chu.

516
00:26:33,650 --> 00:26:35,750
