537
00:27:13,610 --> 00:27:14,830
What should we do?

538
00:27:16,610 --> 00:27:18,910
Let me teach you a lesson, Captain Liang.

539
00:27:32,890 --> 00:27:34,280
Liang Mu Ze, come forward.

540
00:27:34,370 --> 00:27:36,190
My face looks huge. Hurry up.

541
00:27:36,730 --> 00:27:39,310
One, two, three, cheese!

542
00:27:44,730 --> 00:27:46,790
Captain Liang, can you put on a smile?

543
