564
00:29:17,970 --> 00:29:19,590
It's none of my business.

565
00:29:19,980 --> 00:29:29,610
♫ Can't miss a thing about you,
hence there is no regrets ♫

566
00:29:30,090 --> 00:29:34,320
♫ Getting used to your habits
from breakfast to dinner ♫

567
00:29:34,410 --> 00:29:35,360
Do you really enjoy
working in the hospital?

568
00:29:35,450 --> 00:29:36,330
Of course.

569
00:29:43,130 --> 00:29:44,010
Just wait.

570
00:29:46,330 --> 00:29:47,930
I'm so busy with training.

571
00:29:48,010 --> 00:29:48,930
We need to get ready for war too.

572
00:29:49,010 --> 00:29:50,390
I don't have the time to fetch you.

573
00:29:50,810 --> 00:29:52,510
I have legs.

574
00:29:52,730 --> 00:29:53,860
You mean, your broken leg?

575
00:29:54,930 --> 00:29:56,390
I'm a military officer too!

576
00:29:56,530 --> 00:29:57,880
I won't fall behind
even when I lose my flesh and skin.

577
00:29:57,970 --> 00:29:59,670
I'm not as fragile as you think.

578
00:30:02,000 --> 00:30:03,130
Here, let me show you something.

579
00:30:03,210 --> 00:30:04,470
Come here.

580
00:30:04,970 --> 00:30:06,030
See for yourself.

581
00:30:06,530 --> 00:30:07,750
It's pouring.

582
00:30:07,970 --> 00:30:09,700
It's difficult to travel.
How do you plan to go back?

583
00:30:10,050 --> 00:30:10,950
I...

584
00:30:11,290 --> 00:30:12,320
I can drive.

585
00:30:12,410 --> 00:30:13,470
I have a driving licence.

586
00:30:14,320 --> 00:30:15,350
Drive?

587
00:30:17,330 --> 00:30:18,350
What are you doing?

588
00:30:19,370 --> 00:30:20,950
How do you drive?

589
00:30:21,290 --> 00:30:22,750
It's for the sake of your safety.

590
00:30:23,170 --> 00:30:24,340
Be good, Da Miao.

591
00:30:24,770 --> 00:30:25,650
Good girl.

592
00:30:34,090 --> 00:30:34,560
Liang Mu Ze!

593
00:30:34,650 --> 00:30:35,920
If you ever pinch my face again,

594
00:30:36,000 --> 00:30:36,800
I'll chop the 27 bones in your hand

595
00:30:36,880 --> 00:30:38,510
into pieces!

596
00:31:10,690 --> 00:31:11,590
Brigade Commander.

597
00:31:12,130 --> 00:31:14,070
Yes, I'm Liang Mu Ze.

598
00:31:15,010 --> 00:31:16,630
I would like to get your permission
on something.

599
00:31:22,730 --> 00:31:24,710
I'm coming. Stop knocking the door.

600
00:31:27,410 --> 00:31:28,960
Change into the military uniform.
Ten minutes later,

601
00:31:29,040 --> 00:31:30,200
go to the assembly point.

602
00:31:30,290 --> 00:31:31,230
Why?

603
00:31:38,530 --> 00:31:42,430
One, two, three, four.

604
00:31:43,490 --> 00:31:44,750
What's wrong?

605
00:31:46,650 --> 00:31:47,550
You have to run.

606
00:31:48,650 --> 00:31:49,830
What?

607
00:31:50,050 --> 00:31:51,200
Either you run

608
00:31:51,290 --> 00:31:52,870
or you train with them.

609
00:31:57,410 --> 00:31:58,550
Me?

610
00:31:58,640 --> 00:31:59,520
Yes.

611
00:32:00,730 --> 00:32:02,240
Liang Mu Ze, are you crazy?

612
00:32:02,330 --> 00:32:03,320
Hurry up. Do it.

613
00:32:03,410 --> 00:32:04,470
Why?

614
00:32:05,850 --> 00:32:07,110
It's for your own good.

615
00:32:08,250 --> 00:32:09,450
You're not my leader.

616
00:32:09,530 --> 00:32:10,750
Why should I listen to you?

617
00:32:11,210 --> 00:32:12,650
Brigade Commander said
it's just a minor accident

618
00:32:12,730 --> 00:32:13,920
but you injured your leg.

619
00:32:14,010 --> 00:32:15,630
That means you lack training.

620
00:32:15,850 --> 00:32:17,810
Hence, he applied to your superior

621
00:32:17,890 --> 00:32:19,660
to include you in the training
as a non-staff.

622
00:32:20,730 --> 00:32:21,710
What?

623
00:32:21,850 --> 00:32:23,550
It's to strengthen your stamina.

624
00:32:23,930 --> 00:32:25,550
He doesn't want you to get into danger.

625
00:32:26,250 --> 00:32:27,130
But...

626
00:32:27,770 --> 00:32:28,670
Let's go.

627
00:32:29,970 --> 00:32:31,430
I'm an injured person.

628
00:32:31,760 --> 00:32:33,030
You've fully recovered, right?

629
00:32:33,490 --> 00:32:34,370
Let's go.

630
00:32:36,890 --> 00:32:38,630
I can walk on my own.

631
00:32:39,570 --> 00:32:40,750
Here, run now.

632
00:32:42,650 --> 00:32:43,130
Keep running.

633
00:32:43,210 --> 00:32:45,600
Let go of me. I can run on my own.

634
00:32:45,690 --> 00:32:46,870
Run on your own.

635
00:32:48,890 --> 00:32:49,950
Keep running.

636
00:32:50,090 --> 00:32:52,870
One, two, three, four.

637
00:32:53,130 --> 00:32:54,910
Xia Chu, I'll beat you up if I catch you.

638
00:32:55,690 --> 00:32:57,990
-I'm coming.
-I can run on my own!

639
00:33:02,050 --> 00:33:03,520
Stop following me!

640
00:33:03,610 --> 00:33:04,840
When you're in danger,

641
00:33:04,930 --> 00:33:06,670
you should run at first instance, got it?

642
00:33:11,930 --> 00:33:13,520
Watch your arms. Swing your arms.

643
00:33:13,610 --> 00:33:14,710
Keep it low.

644
00:33:19,490 --> 00:33:21,160
Don't stop. Keep running.

645
00:33:21,250 --> 00:33:23,030
I can run on my own!

646
00:33:39,970 --> 00:33:40,850
Try it.

647
00:33:43,210 --> 00:33:44,430
I have to practice shooting too?

648
00:33:44,850 --> 00:33:46,260
It's an order from Brigade Commander.

649
00:33:47,290 --> 00:33:49,390
I've only used a rifle before
when I was in recruit company.

650
00:33:52,690 --> 00:33:53,400
Stand here.

651
00:33:53,490 --> 00:33:55,110
Hit the humanoid target at the front.

652
00:33:56,090 --> 00:33:56,970
Here.

653
00:34:09,210 --> 00:34:10,190
Aim carefully.

654
00:34:10,450 --> 00:34:12,510
Liang Mu Ze, I've never used a gun before.

655
00:34:13,250 --> 00:34:14,750
A gun is not much different from a rifle.

656
00:34:15,050 --> 00:34:17,030
Adjust your breathing and relax.

657
00:34:22,770 --> 00:34:28,399
♫ We'll have ups and downs ♫

658
00:34:29,990 --> 00:34:35,050
♫ The journey to happiness is bound
to be filled with waves ♫

659
00:34:34,810 --> 00:34:35,830
Don't be nervous.

660
00:34:36,680 --> 00:34:42,180
♫ I'm glad we came through the
obstacles that time has brought upon us ♫

661
00:34:38,640 --> 00:34:39,669
Hold the gun firmly.

662
00:34:42,439 --> 00:34:47,939
♫ My hands are still eager
to hold you tight ♫

663
00:34:50,450 --> 00:34:55,899
♫ Nothing matters as long as
our smiles outweigh our tears ♫

664
00:34:57,710 --> 00:35:03,290
♫ Others can doubt me as long as
I have your trust ♫

665
00:35:00,250 --> 00:35:01,310
What do you think?

666
00:35:02,610 --> 00:35:03,800
Liang Mu Ze, look!

667
00:35:03,890 --> 00:35:05,200
If you connect the bullet holes,

668
00:35:03,950 --> 00:35:09,450
♫ Our souls cross paths
as our gaze meet ♫

669
00:35:05,290 --> 00:35:06,390
you can see a heart shape!

670
00:35:09,890 --> 00:35:16,410
♫ Some words you can understand
even if I don't say it ♫

671
00:35:15,410 --> 00:35:16,350
Do it again.

672
00:35:17,290 --> 00:35:23,670
♫ I promise I won't let you slip by ♫

673
00:35:24,020 --> 00:35:30,840
♫ Exchanging everything, we'll become
each other's destiny ♫

674
00:35:26,730 --> 00:35:28,350
Liang Mu Ze is a jerk.

675
00:35:28,850 --> 00:35:30,830
He trained me as if I'm a soldier.

676
00:35:31,050 --> 00:35:32,550
He claimed that he didn't shout at me.

677
00:35:31,500 --> 00:35:37,000
♫ I'll make your heart my kingdom ♫

678
00:35:37,260 --> 00:35:43,820
♫ You and I will make our dream
come true with our lives ♫

679
00:36:08,810 --> 00:36:10,030
Assemble!

680
00:36:23,370 --> 00:36:24,590
One, two, one!

681
00:36:36,730 --> 00:36:37,830
Comrades.

682
00:36:39,130 --> 00:36:40,350
Lately,

683
00:36:41,120 --> 00:36:42,830
the Southeast region of our country

684
00:36:43,610 --> 00:36:44,840
has been experiencing

685
00:36:44,930 --> 00:36:47,150
heavy rain and flood disaster.

686
00:36:48,160 --> 00:36:51,350
In order to protect
the people and their property,

687
00:36:51,810 --> 00:36:53,510
we've been instructed

688
00:36:53,610 --> 00:36:55,110
to aid the disaster areas.

689
00:36:55,730 --> 00:36:57,870
The fighting is going to begin soon.

690
00:36:58,650 --> 00:37:00,310
I only have one requirement.

691
00:37:01,650 --> 00:37:03,230
Confront the danger.

692
00:37:03,560 --> 00:37:06,980
Help and protect the dyke.

693
00:37:07,570 --> 00:37:10,750
Before the rain stops, we won't give up!

694
00:37:11,850 --> 00:37:12,950
Got it?

695
00:37:13,050 --> 00:37:13,950
Yes!

696
00:37:14,410 --> 00:37:15,390
Let's go!

697
00:37:15,530 --> 00:37:17,540
Turn to the rear.

698
00:37:19,450 --> 00:37:21,630
Start marching!

699
00:38:25,370 --> 00:38:26,510
Captain!

700
00:39:41,130 --> 00:39:43,110
Take care!

701
00:40:22,370 --> 00:40:24,790
Take care, Liang Mu Ze.

702
00:40:35,850 --> 00:40:36,850
I'm back.

703
00:40:36,930 --> 00:40:39,670
-You're back.
-Come here.

704
00:40:39,850 --> 00:40:41,440
-Has your leg recovered?
-Are you okay?

705
00:40:41,530 --> 00:40:42,800
I'm okay. I've fully recovered.

706
00:40:42,890 --> 00:40:44,440
-You've recovered.
-What are you doing?

707
00:40:44,520 --> 00:40:46,650
-Reading the flood fighting news.
-Look.

708
00:40:46,730 --> 00:40:48,990
They've been immersed
in the water for many days.

709
00:40:51,490 --> 00:40:52,810
It's stated in the news that
many troops

710
00:40:52,890 --> 00:40:54,030
are rushing to the areas.

711
00:40:54,530 --> 00:40:55,590
Xia Chu.

712
00:40:56,490 --> 00:40:57,160
Dr Zhang.

713
00:40:57,250 --> 00:40:58,230
You're back.

714
00:41:00,480 --> 00:41:01,240
How do you feel?

715
00:41:01,330 --> 00:41:03,390
I've recovered.
I can start working anytime.

716
00:41:03,770 --> 00:41:04,650
That's great.

717
00:41:05,930 --> 00:41:07,230
Is my hairstyle all right?

718
00:41:10,410 --> 00:41:12,870
Dr Zhang, you're...

719
00:41:13,930 --> 00:41:14,950
I'm filming a show.

720
00:41:16,330 --> 00:41:20,150
There is a lady by the name of Mi Gu
from the life channel.

721
00:41:20,530 --> 00:41:21,320
Do you know her?

722
00:41:21,410 --> 00:41:22,950
I know her. She's my best friend.

723
00:41:23,370 --> 00:41:24,490
She wants to produce

724
00:41:24,570 --> 00:41:26,390
a medicine related documentary.

725
00:41:26,890 --> 00:41:28,510
I'll be the main character
in the documentary.

726
00:41:28,730 --> 00:41:30,350
Please work with her.

727
00:41:30,610 --> 00:41:31,490
Don't worry.

728
00:41:34,170 --> 00:41:35,270
Is she single?

729
00:41:36,170 --> 00:41:37,050
Dr Zhang!

730
00:41:47,800 --> 00:41:48,680
Dean.

731
00:41:49,250 --> 00:41:50,390
Allow me to introduce someone to you.

732
00:41:50,810 --> 00:41:52,310
He is Deputy Dean Zhou.

733
00:41:53,610 --> 00:41:54,550
Hello, Deputy Dean Zhou.

734
00:41:55,170 --> 00:41:56,520
Thank you for

735
00:41:56,600 --> 00:41:57,950
being interested in the hospital.

736
00:41:58,250 --> 00:41:59,280
You're so kind, Dean.

737
00:41:59,370 --> 00:42:00,250
We would like to thank you

738
00:42:00,330 --> 00:42:01,830
for supporting our show.

739
00:42:02,290 --> 00:42:03,630
That's our duty.

740
00:42:05,250 --> 00:42:06,130
This is...

741
00:42:06,370 --> 00:42:07,550
I don't think
there's a need to introduce him.

742
00:42:07,690 --> 00:42:08,570
Hello.

743
00:42:10,010 --> 00:42:10,910
Hello.

744
00:42:11,770 --> 00:42:14,080
We decided to film the signing ceremony
at the eleventh hour.

745
00:42:14,170 --> 00:42:15,070
Sorry to have...

746
00:42:17,840 --> 00:42:19,000
I'm sorry. I need to answer a phone call.

747
00:42:19,090 --> 00:42:20,760
Xiao Wen, please communicate
with the other leaders

748
00:42:20,850 --> 00:42:21,760
and Mr Zhuo

749
00:42:21,850 --> 00:42:23,160
regarding the filming details.

750
00:42:23,250 --> 00:42:24,310
Okay, Ms Gu.

751
00:42:28,890 --> 00:42:29,790
Thank you.

752
00:42:33,220 --> 00:42:35,470
[Xia Chu]

753
00:42:56,530 --> 00:42:58,200
I changed Xiao Jun's dressing for you

754
00:42:58,290 --> 00:42:58,880
and you promised

755
00:42:58,970 --> 00:43:01,230
to prepare two weeks worth
of medical orders.

756
00:43:01,850 --> 00:43:02,950
Please honour your words.

757
00:43:27,530 --> 00:43:28,610
It's an honour

758
00:43:28,690 --> 00:43:29,830
to set up a special fund

759
00:43:30,010 --> 00:43:31,630
with the hospital.

760
00:43:32,330 --> 00:43:34,830
We will develop 3D medicine production,

761
00:43:35,090 --> 00:43:36,190
organ printing,

762
00:43:36,770 --> 00:43:38,680
auxiliary instrument printing and so on

763
00:43:38,770 --> 00:43:40,030
in full swing.

764
00:43:40,690 --> 00:43:41,670
We believe that

765
00:43:42,170 --> 00:43:43,280
following the rapid development

766
00:43:43,370 --> 00:43:44,270
of 3D printing,

767
00:43:44,650 --> 00:43:45,840
we will welcome

768
00:43:45,930 --> 00:43:47,430
the new era

769
00:43:47,570 --> 00:43:48,470
of personalised medicine.

770
00:43:54,290 --> 00:43:56,830
Take some scenery shots
in the hospital later.

771
00:43:57,410 --> 00:43:57,800
Sure.

772
00:43:57,890 --> 00:43:59,230
I hope everything
goes according to plan.

773
00:44:01,210 --> 00:44:01,760
-Goodbye.
-Goodbye.

774
00:44:01,850 --> 00:44:02,730
I'll see you off.

775
00:44:05,290 --> 00:44:06,760
How long will the filming take?

776
00:44:06,850 --> 00:44:08,200
Let's go for dinner tonight.

777
00:44:08,290 --> 00:44:09,990
Should I wait for you?

778
00:44:20,170 --> 00:44:21,470
Are you not going to join
the photography session?

779
00:44:22,930 --> 00:44:24,030
Why should I join?

780
00:44:24,250 --> 00:44:25,820
He's young and talented.

781
00:44:31,250 --> 00:44:32,130
I'm sorry.

782
00:44:32,610 --> 00:44:33,710
Please hold on.

783
00:44:34,210 --> 00:44:35,090
Mi Gu.

784
00:44:37,090 --> 00:44:38,140
Let's go for dinner tonight.

785
00:44:38,610 --> 00:44:39,590
I'll invite Xia Chu too.

786
00:44:40,090 --> 00:44:41,190
Dr Zhang, please join us.

787
00:44:41,290 --> 00:44:42,170
Sure.

788
00:44:45,490 --> 00:44:46,480
I have something to do at night.

789
00:44:46,570 --> 00:44:47,450
Well...

790
00:44:48,010 --> 00:44:49,990
Dr Zhang, don't we have a date?

791
00:44:55,890 --> 00:44:57,030
I'm sorry. I forgot that.

792
00:44:57,400 --> 00:44:58,910
We have a discussion.

793
00:45:02,490 --> 00:45:03,750
I'll not take up your time then.

794
00:45:03,850 --> 00:45:04,910
I'm leaving.

795
00:45:11,010 --> 00:45:12,270
Why did you do that?
